Melt margarine in large saucepan over low heat. Add marshmallows and stir until completely melted. Remove from heat. Add KELLOGG's RICE KRISPIES cereal. Stir until well coated. Using 1/2 cup measure coated with cooking spray, portion warm mixture and using buttered hands shape into snowball. Place coconut into large bowl. Roll snowball in coconut until well coated. Sprinkle ball with powdered sugar. Best if served the same day.